cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.GT

This paper proposes a new architecture for Deep Reinforcement Learning, specifically for the Atari 2600 domain. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks and their architecture, which suggests the category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with image processing and computer vision, which could place it in the category cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of reinforcement learning and optimization techniques could also place it in the categories cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory).
